757
01:21:00,541 --> 01:21:01,833
Bawa temanmu.

758
01:21:04,416 --> 01:21:05,708
Aku mau melihat wajahnya.

759
01:22:39,666 --> 01:22:42,166
Perabotanmu tak banyak, Estrada.

760
01:22:59,916 --> 01:23:01,625
Kalahkanlah mereka.

761
